headline: Northern Trust (NTRS) Stock Is Up, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of financial services company Northern Trust (NASDAQ:NTRS) jumped 3.5% in the morning session after Wells Fargo raised its price target on the stock to $145 from $131.
